data.description: Beautiful Extended Cape on a large property. Living room with a cathedral celling and two skylights leads to a formal dining room and large open eat-in-kitchen. 2 bedrooms and full bathroom on the first floor. Second floor features primary bedroom with walk-in closet and full bathroom and additional open room perfect for a home office. Full partially finished basement with plenty of storage and separate entrance. Roof and heating system only 2 years old. Large fence in backyard. Convenient to LIRR Train Station, parks beaches and easy access to parkways. And much much more....
